Sentencas: Mn1.5Co1.5O4 spinel oxide as a cathode or one component of a composite cathode presents no visible reaction with an Y2O3-stabilized ZrO2 electrolyte.
Titulo: Novel Mn1.5Co1.5O4 spinel cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The low electrode polarization resistances and good performance compared with traditional Sr-doped LaMnO3-YSZ composite cathodes imply promising application for the next generation of intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Novel Mn1.5Co1.5O4 spinel cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
